---
layout: default
---
%header#overview.jumbotron.subhead
  .row
    .span6
      %h1 
        %i.icon-book
        JavaDoc
      %p.lead Automatically generated Java documentation for PerfCake.
    .span6
      .well{:style => "padding: 25px 25px 15px 25px;"}
        %span{:style => "display: block; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1em;"} Did you already try the other guides?
        %span{:style => "display: block;"}
          %ul
            %li
              %i.icon-time
              %a{:href => "#{site.base_url}/quickstart"} Quickstart Example 
              \- run your first benchmark in 5 minutes
            %li
              %a{:href => "#{site.base_url}/guide/started"} Getting started guide
            %li
              %a{:href => "#{site.base_url}/guide/user"} Users' guide
            %li
              %a{:href => "#{site.base_url}/guide/devel"} Developers' guide
            -# %li
            -#   %a{:href => "#{site.base_url}/javadoc"} JavaDoc
        %div{:style => "clear:both"}
  .row
    .span12
      .page-header
        %h2 
          %i.icon-download
          JavaDoc downloads
        %p
          Current version of JavaDoc from the master branch is 0.2-SNAPSHOT and can be downloaded as a
          %a.btn.btn-primary.btn-big{:href => "http://javadoc.perfcake.org/perfcake-0.2-SNAPSHOT-javadoc.jar"} 
            %i.icon-archive
            JavaDoc Archive &raquo;
        %p
          You can also read the documentation online
          %a.btn.btn-primary.btn-big{:href => "http://javadoc.perfcake.org/", :target => "_blank"} 
            %i.icon-book
            Online JavaDoc &raquo;
        %p
          As a developer, you might be also interested in our 
          %a.btn.btn-primary.btn-big{:href => "#{site.base_url}/community"} 
            %i.icon-group
            Community &raquo;
        %p 
          If you found the JavaDoc insufficient, we cannot encourage you enough to contribute 
          = succeed "." do
            %a{:href => "https://github.com/PerfCake/PerfCake/issues?state=open"} a fix
        .alert.alert-error
          %i.icon-info-sign
          %strong Downloads for older versions will be available too.
